```plantuml
@startuml Nishu0_anime_nft_marketplace

actor User
participant "NFTContext" as Context
participant "NFTMarketplace.sol" as Contract
participant "IPFS"
participant "Metamask"

User -> Context: Connect Wallet
Context -> Metamask: Request Account Access
Metamask -> User: Prompt for Access
User -> Metamask: Grant Access
Metamask -> Context: Provide Account Info

User -> Context: Mint New NFT
Context -> IPFS: Upload Image & Metadata
IPFS -> Context: Return IPFS URI
Context -> Contract: Call createToken(IPFS URI)
Contract -> Contract: Register NFT & URI

User -> Context: List NFT for Sale
Context -> Contract: Call listNFTForSale(tokenId, price)
Contract -> Contract: Set Sale Price

User -> Context: Buy NFT
Context -> Metamask: Sign Transaction
Metamask -> User: Request Transaction Signature
User -> Metamask: Sign Transaction
Metamask -> Context: Transaction Hash
Context -> Contract: Call buyNFT(tokenId)
Contract -> Contract: Transfer Ownership

User -> Context: View Owned NFTs
Context -> Contract: Call fetchOwnedNFTs(userAddress)
Contract -> Context: Return NFT List

@enduml
```